  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Actually, I believe I went to school, but I don't have really any clear memories of that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we start walking again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we walked towards home again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was walking towards home, primarily because people were interested in who-- in survivors, because that was the only place where you know you could meet people who remained alive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the way, my paternal grandparents both died before the war ended.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My maternal grandmother survived, but she got gangrene on one of her fingers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a-- an unbelievable sight to see how this finger is withering away on a live body, and eventually just fell off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How and why it didn't attack the rest of her hand, I'll never know, but it didn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course when we got home, we were all like skeletons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And because our house was one of the better ones in town, with flowing water and all this, when we got there, we found the firemen had occupied the house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they told us that before that, there was a German hospital in the house, and there was a-- later was a Russian hospital in the house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the firemen came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So obviously there wasn't a stitch of anything left from our belongings, money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I don't believe that in any other house there was either, because the-- the local population would just come in and plunder everything out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "However, before we left, my father boarded up [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some corners in the attic and stuffed in a lot of things there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Among them were needles from his store, sugar, soap, toothpaste, all kinds of these things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The jewelery he buried under a tree in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
